08:07.181 --> 08:17.152
Isaiah wants to target those who are feeling way down, worn out, run down from the burdens in their lives.

08:17.192 --> 08:21.237
Those who are struggling and stumbling, he wants them to take heart.

08:21.577 --> 08:24.100
God is about to reveal something big.

08:24.661 --> 08:27.544
So discouraged heart, disappointed heart, perk up.

08:28.545 --> 08:29.586
Lift your head.

08:30.146 --> 08:31.048
and be encouraged.

08:33.472 --> 08:39.362
