08:53.890 --> 08:58.636
All people are like grass and all their faithfulness is like the flowers of the field.

08:58.696 --> 09:03.002
The grass withers and the flowers fall because the breath of the Lord blows on them.

09:03.563 --> 09:05.025
Surely the people are grass.

09:05.426 --> 09:10.773
The grass withers and the flowers fall, but the word of our God endures what people?

09:11.434 --> 09:11.954
Forever.

09:11.974 --> 09:20.626
See, God is not calling us to place our hope in some sort of human ingenuity.

09:21.794 --> 09:31.243
He's not asking us to trust others like government or politicians or the latest technology.

09:31.283 --> 09:37.950
