09:39.551 --> 09:46.398
You see, the charge to take heart, to take comfort is not based on the power of positive thinking.

09:47.479 --> 09:50.642
It's not about pulling yourself up by your own bootstraps.

09:50.786 --> 10:00.175
or practicing the latest principles of Tony Robbins or any other successes in the mind or power positive thinking motivational podcast.

10:01.997 --> 10:03.098
Friends, here's the reality.

10:03.378 --> 10:05.020
Life is crazy at times.

10:05.380 --> 10:06.381
Crazy.

10:08.423 --> 10:11.886
Men's efforts have very finite limits.

10:12.527 --> 10:13.268
You know this.

10:14.289 --> 10:15.370
We're like grass.

10:15.430 --> 10:17.111
We're like the grass in these foothills.

10:17.812 --> 10:19.794
Boy, if you come through here in the spring, you're like,

10:19.906 --> 10:21.288
This is so beautiful.

10:21.408 --> 10:23.532
It's so green rolling hills.

10:24.133 --> 10:25.274
Well, just come back in June.

10:26.917 --> 10:27.157
Right?

10:27.418 --> 10:30.963
Whenever we had a higher staff, I always try to candidate him like, you know, in April, May.

10:32.405 --> 10:34.008
One guy asked me, is it always look like this?

10:34.048 --> 10:41.820
I'm like, oh, yeah.

10:41.840 --> 10:43.683
Isaiah makes a powerful contrast here.

10:44.504 --> 10:48.370
He contrasts the helplessness of humankind

10:49.666 --> 10:53.550
with the infinitely powerful word and presence of God.

10:54.270 --> 10:55.091
Friends, here's the point.

10:56.072 --> 11:08.084
The basis for taking heart in all of this, the basis for being encouraged and taking comfort is because the unfailing, everlasting word of God is behind it.

11:08.925 --> 11:09.225
Yay?

11:11.427 --> 11:13.829
There's no sure guarantee than that.

11:14.950 --> 11:18.674
Always remember this, God's word is his work

11:19.074 --> 11:20.015
is his person.

11:21.617 --> 11:25.723
Theology 101, God's Word is his work, is his person.

11:25.743 --> 11:30.268
There's no difference between what he says he will do and what he does.

11:32.171 --> 11:39.460
All our efforts as people are finite, limited, and frail, but friends, God is absolutely majestic in everlasting.

11:41.823 --> 11:43.986
When he says it, he's doing it.

11:45.442 --> 11:49.968
