Man, as I said in the past weeks, our series in Isaiah, I think you will agree, we've heard a tremendous number of tough warnings, right?

12:37.685 --> 12:42.290
Tough warnings, judgments being declared from God, but now

12:43.490 --> 12:49.058
More clearly and loudly than the word of judgment, the word of comfort and hope is to be proclaimed.

12:51.021 --> 12:59.012
Certainly God is all powerful and majestic, the God of the universe, but though he is that, he is gentle like a shepherd.

